# UI Suggestions

Custom UI suggestions allow users to configure additional UIs for specific aliases, servers, and variables.

## View alias with no UI suggestions configured
Tags: ui-suggestions

* Start the app with boot configuration
* Navigate to "/aliases/ai"
* Page contains "No additional UIs"
* Page contains "Configure custom UIs"
* Page contains "/variables/uis"

## View server with no UI suggestions configured
Tags: ui-suggestions

* Start the app with boot configuration
* Navigate to "/servers/ai_stub"
* Click on "Details" tab
* Page contains "No additional UIs"
* Page contains "/variables/uis"

## View variable with no UI suggestions configured
Tags: ui-suggestions

